==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intangible
<hw>In*tan"gi*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>tangible</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>intangible</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not tangible; incapable of being
touched; not perceptible to the touch; impalpable; imperceptible.</def>
<rj><au>Bp. Wilkins.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A corporation is an artificial, invisible, <qex>intangible</qex>
being.</q> <rj><qau>Marshall.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>In*tan"gi*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>In*tan"gi*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intangle</ent>⟦br⟧
